[node name="Level4" type="Node3D"]
editor_description = "Room 04 — The Final Kick. Two chambers: the front room holds the ball's start and the interlocked gears, slightly off-axis behind a short domino run; a divider wall with a center gap (doorway) leads into the back chamber, where the wire chain and the final vial sit — with crates nearby to send flying on detonation. Last level; clearing it leads to the ending screen."

